headline: How Dividend Stability and Caesars Lease Concerns Will Impact VICI Properties (VICI) Investors
summary: VICI Properties Inc. previously declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of US$0.45 per share for the October–December 2025 period, payable on January 8, 2026 to shareholders of record as of December 17, 2025.
